    <div class="sector-test-info">
        <div class="wrap">

			<div class="info-title">베타 테스터 정보 입력</div>
 
			<div class="info-login">
				<p class="nomember">에듀윌 회원이신가요?<a href="javascript:;">로그인하기</a></p>
			</div>

			<div class="alert">
